Application: Cascade-Restrict Deadlock Diamond
  Description: Diamond pattern - two cascade-incoming and one restrict-incoming on the same node (TERMIN-S codes d)
Id: a1c0c1a0-cade-4a00-9000-000000000014

Identity:
  Scopes are "dm.view", "dm.manage"
  A "tester" has "dm.view" and "dm.manage"

Content called "roots":
  Each root has a label which is text, required
  Anyone with "dm.view" can view roots
  Anyone with "dm.manage" can create roots

Content called "branches":
  Each branch has a label which is text, required
  Each branch has a root which references roots, required, cascade on delete
  Anyone with "dm.view" can view branches
  Anyone with "dm.manage" can create branches

Content called "twigs":
  Each twig has a label which is text, required
  Each twig has a branch which references branches, required, cascade on delete
  Each twig has an alt branch which references branches, cascade on delete
  Anyone with "dm.view" can view twigs
  Anyone with "dm.manage" can create twigs

Content called "leaves":
  Each leaf has a label which is text, required
  Each leaf has a branch which references branches, required, restrict on delete
  Anyone with "dm.view" can view leaves
  Anyone with "dm.manage" can create leaves
